Package: demulticoder
Title: An R package for the integrated analyis of multiplex metabarcodes 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Martha", "Sudermann", , "sudermam@oregonstate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A wrapper package to filter, trim primers, and denoise metabarcoding data using Cutadapt and the dada2 R package. The package can handle datasets that contain pooled amplicons, or simpler experimental designs
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
